title: Beanie Sigel + Classic Interviews
itunes:title: Beanie Sigel + Classic Interviews
description:
Tues 12/27- As 2017 approaches, the Breakfast Club is giving their best interviews of 2016. One of the most heated interviews of the year featured Beanie Sigel who was beefin with Meek Mill who was also beefin with The Game (confused?) Also, Envy, Angela and Charlamagne sit down with Tracy Morgan, Stevie J. and more. Charlamagne awards himself with Donkey of the Day and Katt Williams as well.
